33 A BILL
34 TO BE ENTITLED
35 AN ACT
36
37 Relating to public employees; to amend Sections 16-22-6
38 and 36-1-4.4, Code of Alabama 1975; to prohibit salary
39 deductions from certain education employees for labor
40 organizations; to prohibit employee organizations and
41 professional associations from prohibiting or limiting any
42 state employee's ability to revoke his or her membership; and
43 to further provide for the procedures relating to salary
44 deductions, including termination of deductions, for all state
45 employees.
46 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
47 Section 1. Sections 16-22-6 and 36-1.4.4, Code of
48 Alabama 1975, are amended to read as follows:
